1. Install Ansible on Learer First
   sudo bash main.sh -> menu 1. Install Ansible
2. Declare leader and worker in 2 files: inventory_pre.ini and config.env and then run without sudo
   bash main.sh -> menu 2
   a. Create vault file:
ansible_user: ubuntu
ansible_password: qwe123

3. Add public key of controller to leader
cat ./id_rsa.pub >> ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
